    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Rhodiola humilis are anxiety, fatigue, depression, and insomnia, which are often caused by chronic stress that can lead to adrenal fatigue, a condition where the adrenal glands do not produce enough hormones to manage stress, and hypertension, a condition characterized by high blood pressure. Rhodiola humilis has also been shown to alleviate burnout, a state of emotional, mental, and physical exhaustion, and digestive issues, such as bloating and irritable bowel syndrome, by regulating gut bacteria and improving gut health. Additionally, this plant has been used to treat chronic fatigue syndrome, a long-term illness characterized by persistent fatigue, and hypothyroidism, a condition where the thyroid gland does not produce enough hormones. Rhodiola humilis has also been shown to improve migraines, a neurological condition characterized by severe headaches, and mental fatigue, a condition where an individual feels tired and lacks motivation, often accompanied by mood swings. Furthermore, Rhodiola humilis has been used to treat hypoglycemia, a condition where blood sugar levels are too low, and cognitive decline, a condition where memory and cognitive function are impaired.",
